name: Similarity
description: This work was done against the backdrop of growing tensions and alarm calls from the leadership of both countries.  Gagging, promoting any laws, painful retention of power - these points have become commonplace for us. Moreover, it seems that many already do not see anything terrible in this. After all, everything is done under a delicious sauce "for the good".  Once again we are building walls and protecting our braces. And what are these braces?  And do we still need a strong and powerful king's hand?
